<section id="projects">
    <h2>Portfolio Projects</h2>

    <div class="project">
        <h3>Product Case Study: Improving Bug Reporting Efficiency</h3>
        <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Bug reporting was inconsistent and time-consuming, leading to delays in issue resolution.</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Redesigned the bug reporting feature with streamlined workflows, clear categorization, and built-in templates.</p>
        <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Reduced bug reporting time by 40% and improved developer response rates by 25%.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
        <h3>User Persona Creation for E-commerce Platform</h3>
        <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Understand user pain points in the checkout process.</p>
        <p><strong>Actions:</strong> Conducted surveys with 50+ users and created detailed personas.</p>
        <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Provided actionable insights that informed the redesign of the checkout flow.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
        <h3>Product Roadmap: Mobile App Feature Rollout</h3>
        <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Plan the release of a new "Saved Searches" feature for a real estate app.</p>
        <p><strong>Actions:</strong> Created a 6-month roadmap with milestones, dependencies, and success metrics.</p>
        <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Delivered a clear timeline to stakeholders, facilitating smooth execution.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
        <h3>Competitive Analysis: Task Management Tools</h3>
        <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Identify gaps in current task management tools to propose new features.</p>
        <p><strong>Actions:</strong> Analyzed 5 popular tools and highlighted areas for differentiation.</p>
        <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Proposed two feature ideas, one of which was adopted in the product roadmap.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
        <h3>Product Requirement Document: Chatbot Integration</h3>
        <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Define requirements for integrating a chatbot into a customer service portal.</p>
        <p><strong>Actions:</strong> Drafted objectives, scope, user stories, and acceptance criteria.</p>
        <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Reduced development time by 15% with a clear understanding of the feature.</p>
    </div>
</section>

